 {"id":"bd-3ar8v.2.13","title":"[Phase 1][Perf] Consolidate session incremental append into single-buffer serialization","description":"Replaced Vec<Vec<u8>> (N allocations) with single Vec<u8> buffer in session incremental append path. Uses serde_json::to_writer directly into buffer, eliminates N intermediate to_vec() allocations. Background thread writes entire buffer in one write_all() call instead of N separate writes, reducing syscall overhead.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"OpusCode","created_at":"2026-02-16T22:57:59.228755815Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-16T22:59:05.838925170Z","closed_at":"2026-02-16T22:59:05.838827889Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["perf-3x","phase-1","session"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.13","depends_on_id":"bd-3ar8v.2","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-16T22:57:59.228755815Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}],"comments":[{"id":1890,"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.13","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"Implemented and committed (555758c3). Changed incremental append path from Vec<Vec<u8>> to single Vec<u8> buffer. to_vec() per entry replaced with to_writer() into shared buffer. Background thread now does single write_all() instead of N writes through BufWriter. cargo check --all-targets clean, cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings clean.","created_at":"2026-02-16T22:58:53Z"}]}
 {"id":"bd-3ar8v.2.14","title":"[Phase 1][Support] De-box session-index async update queue hot path","description":"Optimize SessionIndex async snapshot indexing path by removing per-enqueue heap boxing in IndexUpdateCommand::Enqueue and switching to value transport while preserving retry and coalescing semantics. Scope: src/session_index.rs plus focused tests.","notes":"Implemented in src/session_index.rs: IndexUpdateCommand::Enqueue now carries PendingIndexUpdate by value (removed Box allocation on enqueue hot path), dispatcher arm updated, send/fallback path updated, and targeted clippy allow on enum with rationale to preserve de-box optimization under -D warnings.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"StormyBridge","created_at":"2026-02-16T23:50:21.600895987Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-17T00:17:36.962975060Z","closed_at":"2026-02-17T00:17:36.962950484Z","close_reason":"Completed: de-boxed IndexUpdateCommand enqueue path in src/session_index.rs and validated with rch cargo check --all-targets; clippy -D warnings currently has unrelated pre-existing failure in tests/bench_scenario_runner.rs (too_many_lines).","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.14","depends_on_id":"bd-3ar8v.2","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-16T23:50:21.600895987Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
